'''Dayta group''' was a pair of [[Delta-class DX-9 stormtrooper transport]]s in commercial hands ferrying workers that passed close to the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[XQ1 Platform]] [[Outpost D-34]] shortly after the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]]. During their transit of the station's jurisdiction, a flight of [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE/LN starfighters]] led by [[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]] scanned them for contraband but found nothing. However, a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] refugees from [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]] were discovered aboard the one of the [[BFF-1 bulk freighter/Legends|bulk freighters]] of [[Onece group|''Onece'']] group that were passing through the checkpoint at the same time. Transports ''Dayta'' made a swift exit into hyperspace once raiders entered the system the shooting began.

